  "texts": [
    "Put together, these components allow ScanEZ to deliver superior performance in spatial scanpath prediction, and efficiency in the modeling of its temporal dimension.",
    "Evaluations on EML We analyze the performance of ScanEZ and its ablated variants on the EML dataset (Caruso et al., 2022).",
    "Once more, pretraining yields pronounced improvements across metrics (Table 1: Top: comparison between our framework and Eyettention on the CELER L1 dataset (CLR) to our model trained on: only EZ-Reader data (w/o Fine-tuning), only human data (w/o Pre-training)",
    ", and with both pre-training on EZ-Reader and then fune-tuning on human data (ScanEZ).",
    "Bottom: evaluation using the EML dataset."
  ]
}